0.1.1

Usage: dotnet-newclass [arguments] [options]

Arguments:
  name of class(required)         

Options:
  --version                       Show version information
  -?|-h|--help                    generating C# class file from razor template
  -t|--template <TEMPLATEFILE>    razor template file, '-' means get from standard input, default is following:
                                  -----------------
                                  using System;
                                  using System.Collections.Generic;
                                  using System.Linq;
                                  using System.Threading.Tasks;
                                  
                                  namespace @Model.Namespace
                                  {
                                      public class @Model.ClassName
                                      {
                                      }
                                  }
                                  -----------------

  -a|--properties <NAME>=<VALUE>  additional properties for razor(can be accessed by @Model.Properties["<NAME>"])
  -n|--namespace <NAMESPACE>      class namespace(default: current directory name)
  -o|--output <OUTPUTFILEPATH>    path to output file(default: standard output)
  -e|--encoding <ENCODING>        file content encoding(default: UTF-8)

